50|$|The Red <b>Flag</b> <b>Canal</b> was {{considered}} to be a great achievement of the Chinese workers in the 1960s and was the subject of several movies. The Red <b>Flag</b> <b>Canal</b> was featured in propaganda both internal and external to China, as an exemplar of what workers could achieve and local mass initiative.|$|R
